parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to replace the Takata airbag can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the timing chain and solenoid can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fracture of the lower control arm can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: A loud popping noise is heard while turning the steering wheel
